WEBVTT

00:04:58.320 --> 00:05:00.936
So with the anonymity of the internet,

00:05:00.960 --> 00:05:02.176
I went undercover.

00:05:02.200 --> 00:05:05.536
(Laughter)

00:05:05.560 --> 00:05:09.320
I set up this ghost profile
and went crazy.

00:05:10.360 --> 00:05:14.136
Now, on a practical level,
it was very simple,

00:05:14.160 --> 00:05:16.936
but on an emotional level,
it was kind of daunting,

00:05:16.960 --> 00:05:20.376
especially with the racist vitriol
that I had experienced.

00:05:20.400 --> 00:05:24.856
But what I didn't realize
is that my trolls were inoculating me,

00:05:24.880 --> 00:05:26.496
thickening my skin,

00:05:26.520 --> 00:05:30.336
making me immune to viewpoints
that I didn't necessarily agree with,